# Billets PDF

## Specs
- Format : 420×210pts (A6 paysage — taille réelle boarding pass)
- Nommage : `billet-TO7020-{Prenom}-{NOM}.pdf`
- Téléchargement : INDIVIDUEL — jamais de ZIP

## Données vols
```typescript
const FLIGHT_DATA = {
  aller:  { code:'TO7020', from:'ORY', fromCity:'Paris Orly',        to:'TLN', toCity:'Toulon Hyères',  dep:'09:45', arr:'11:15', date:'03 JUL 2025' },
  retour: { code:'AF7315', from:'NCE', fromCity:'Nice Côte d\'Azur', to:'CDG', toCity:'Paris CDG',      dep:'17:55', arr:'19:30', date:'05 JUL 2025' },
}
```

## Couleurs PDF
```js
bg:'#1A1612', text:'#F5E6C8', accent:'#C9A84C', muted:'#7a6e64', enfant:'#B76E79'
```

## Téléchargement client
```typescript
import { pdf } from '@react-pdf/renderer';
const blob = await pdf(<BoardingPassPDF {...props} />).toBlob();
const url = URL.createObjectURL(blob);
const a = document.createElement('a');
a.href = url;
a.download = `billet-${flightCode}-${prenom}-${nom.toUpperCase()}.pdf`;
a.click();
URL.revokeObjectURL(url);
```
